text: Desmiphora canescens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1874. It is known from Colombia, Mexico, and Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora canescens. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1874
